  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2607200/extras/0852ebcddc4a0b15d4f297fc0838240b.avif?t=1705473765\" width=553 height=132 /></span><br>One Button Run is a casual game in which a sparrow touches an apple using only one button.<br>Meet 4 stages and various animal friends!<br><br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2607200/extras/a9bada69f88781f7990b30dd78fe5850.avif?t=1705473765\" width=600 height=338 /></span><br>1. Select a map!<br><br><br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2607200/extras/65f9b677c828cb91f4ab9d9915faf750.avif?t=1705473765\" width=600 height=338 /></span><br>2. Press the space bar to return to the starting point.<br><br><br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2607200/extras/8decaa30612f64f7a41b9476e48d3689.avif?t=1705473765\" width=600 height=338 /></span><br>3. Touching the apple, you can clear the game!<br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2607200/extras/ad1fd48eefb0a52f48c249b94c227387.avif?t=1705473765\" width=600 height=338 /></span><br>In addition to the single mode, there is also [VS MODE] for two players to enjoy with one PC!<br><br><br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2607200/extras/af7af363298f2bc5391df38b55955029.avif?t=1705473765\" width=600 height=338 /></span><br>Enjoy with your loving family, lovers, friends, and boss!",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2607200/extras/0852ebcddc4a0b15d4f297fc0838240b.avif?t=1705473765\" width=553 height=132 /></span><br>One Button Run is a casual game in which a sparrow touches an apple using only one button.<br>Meet 4 stages and various animal friends!<br><br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2607200/extras/a9bada69f88781f7990b30dd78fe5850.avif?t=1705473765\" width=600 height=338 /></span><br>1. Select a map!<br><br><br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2607200/extras/65f9b677c828cb91f4ab9d9915faf750.avif?t=1705473765\" width=600 height=338 /></span><br>2. Press the space bar to return to the starting point.<br><br><br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2607200/extras/8decaa30612f64f7a41b9476e48d3689.avif?t=1705473765\" width=600 height=338 /></span><br>3. Touching the apple, you can clear the game!<br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2607200/extras/ad1fd48eefb0a52f48c249b94c227387.avif?t=1705473765\" width=600 height=338 /></span><br>In addition to the single mode, there is also [VS MODE] for two players to enjoy with one PC!<br><br><br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2607200/extras/af7af363298f2bc5391df38b55955029.avif?t=1705473765\" width=600 height=338 /></span><br>Enjoy with your loving family, lovers, friends, and boss!",
